        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: OSD layer cleanup for OI scrub",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: OSD layer cleanup for OI scrub\n\nBackport of commit: I3e6880271ee73ec2c4638b02c7e9c55fc827bdf3.\n\n1) Abstract some common functions in OSD layer.\n2) Call lu_object_put() in osd_object_find() under failure case.\n3) Do not release buffer_head until all the needed contents have\n   been accessed in osd_oi_index_create_one().\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <laisiyao@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I146e78bb68725b32fff12de8050b6daefb9800f1\n"
      },
